          "title": "Building Permits",
          "path": "/services/building-permits",
          "body": {
            "processed": "<p>All new construction, renovations, and structural modifications in Willowbrook require a building permit. Our Building Department reviews applications to ensure compliance with local zoning regulations and building codes.</p><h2>How to Apply</h2><ul><li>Complete the building permit application form</li><li>Submit architectural plans and site surveys</li><li>Pay the applicable permit fee</li><li>Schedule required inspections</li></ul>",
            "summary": "All new construction, renovations, and structural modifications in Willowbrook require a building permit. Our Building Department reviews applications to ensure compliance with local zoning regulation"
          },
