          "path": "/services/water-billing",
          "body": {
            "processed": "<p>The Town of Willowbrook provides water and sewer services to all residents. Bills are issued quarterly based on metered water usage. We offer online payment, automatic bank draft, and in-person payment options.</p><h2>Payment Options</h2><ul><li>Online payment portal</li><li>Automatic bank draft enrollment</li><li>In-person at Town Hall</li><li>Mail payment to P.O. Box 1847</li></ul>",
