          "title": "Trash & Recycling",
          "path": "/services/trash-and-recycling",
          "body": {
            "processed": "<p>Curbside trash and recycling collection is provided weekly to all Willowbrook residents. The town also operates a drop-off recycling center for materials not accepted in curbside collection.</p><h2>Collection Schedule</h2><ul><li>Trash: Every Tuesday</li><li>Recycling: Every Thursday</li><li>Yard waste: First and third Saturdays (April - November)</li><li>Bulk pickup: By appointment</li></ul>",
            "summary": "Curbside trash and recycling collection is provided weekly to all Willowbrook residents. The town also operates a drop-off recycling center for materials not accepted in curbside collection.Collection"
